            <section class="content-section" id="problem">
                <h2>User Problem</h2>
                <p>Users needed an elegant way to interact with their robot vacuum via Google Home and Alexa.</p>
                
                <p>The designers on my team and my agency needed to develop best-practices for voice skill design.</p>
                            
